’گگعTitle: Regular Expressions
Path: Regular Expressions
Content:
Regular expressions in Nushell's commands are handled by the 
``rust-lang/regex``
 crate. If you want to know more, check the crate documentation: "
[link: https://github.com/rust-lang/regex] regex
".
